issue fixture design).\n\n## Suggestions for the REVIEW agent\n- Verify `--help` works without go installed (help is parsed before `need go`)\n- The issue fixture relies on `go vet` detecting `Printf` format mismatch — confirm this triggers on the reviewer's Go version\n- `staticcheck` step correctly SKIPs when not installed (doesn't fail the run)\n- `FMT_MODE` CI override is tested implicitly through the clean fixture (which runs with default auto mode = fix locally)\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
